I went back to the club hotel after dinner with the sporting director. I knew the following day I had the medical and then the contract with the president so I was nervous and I didn&rsquo;t want to sleep so I went to the hotel bar with my brother for a coffee.<br />
<br />
&lsquo;The woman who is now my wife was serving. It was January 27 and so there were still four days left of the transfer market. Another team called me and were prepared to lay-on a private plane for me to go and sign for them. I said to my brother: &ldquo;No, I&rsquo;ve given my word to the Sevilla president; I&rsquo;m going to sign the contract tomorrow&hellip; and I&rsquo;m going to marry that waitress&rdquo;.&rsquo;
